"Well, if you want we can help you in another attack" he begins, but isnt
able to finish. He receives a comm-link from Speedbreaker saying that they
have company. "Something is going on outside," he states as he runs
outside. He sees the Cr chamber, and Dead End in it, and his cycle is
complete. He opens it, "Come Dead End, it may be and enemy attack" he
states, he then sees Beastbox and Squawktalk, "You too, come on" he
finishes.
